          </p>
          <p class="text-subtle">Your domain will be registered through Enom, an ICANN accredited domain registrar. Registering a domain you agree to the <a href="/registration-agreement?account_id=76691">Domain Registration Agreement</a>.</p>
        </div>

        
      </form>

           <!-- <trying new form> -->

          <div>
            <%=form_for(@domain, :url=> url_for(:controller => 'domains/registers', :action => 'create'), html: { method: :post }) do |form| %>
